2014年2月24日，宣布，索尼與Escape Artists計劃打算拍一部續集，並再由李察·溫克編劇<ref>{{cite news|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|title=Sequel to Denzel Washington Thriller ‘Equalizer’ Moves Forward as Sony Brings Back Writer Richard Wenk|url=http://www.thewrap.com/equalizer-2-moving-forward-sony-brings-back-screenwriter-richard-wenk-exclusive/|accessdate=February 25, 2014|publisher=thewrap.com|date=February 24, 2014|archive-date=2016-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508023804/http://www.thewrap.com/equalizer-2-moving-forward-sony-brings-back-screenwriter-richard-wenk-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/the-equalizer-2-sequel-denzel-washington/|title=Sony Developing THE EQUALIZER 2 Following Positive Test Scores; Denzel Washington Expected to Return|work=Collider|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|date=February 24, 2014|accessdate=2014-06-27|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001230143/http://collider.com/the-equalizer-2-sequel-denzel-washington/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flicksandbits.com/2014/02/24/the-equalizer-2-moving-forward-after-positive-test-screenings-denzel-washington-expected-to-return/65847/|work=Flicks and Bits|title=‘The Equalizer 2′ Moving Forward After Positive Test Screenings; Denzel Washington Expected To Return|date=February 24, 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301183536/http://www.flicksandbits.com/2014/02/24/the-equalizer-2-moving-forward-after-positive-test-screenings-denzel-washington-expected-to-return/65847/|archivedate=2014年3月1日|accessdate=2014年6月27日}}</ref>。2014年10月上旬，法奎接受記者採訪時表示，會有續集的原因是當觀眾和丹佐所期望的。他說，這將會有一個有趣的人物和能有更多國際風味的續集<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lang|first1=Brent|title=‘Equalizer’ Director Antoine Fuqua: ‘I Don’t Believe I Should Filter the Violence’|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/features/antoine-fuqua-equalizer-director-1201317570/|accessdate=October 5, 2014|publisher=variety.com|date=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007045958/http://variety.com/2014/film/features/antoine-fuqua-equalizer-director-1201317570/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月22日，續集獲得片商證實，華盛頓將再度回歸演出<ref>{{cite news |last1= |first1= |title=‘Equalizer’ Getting Sequel |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/the-equalizer-sequel-denzel-washington-1201477930/ |accessdate=April 23, 2015 |publisher=variety.com |date=April 22, 2015 |archive-date=2015-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150425183945/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/the-equalizer-sequel-denzel-washington-1201477930/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年6月11日，索尼宣布《私刑教育2》（The Equalizer 2）在2017年9月29日推出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://collider.com/the-equalizer-2-release-date/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-06-12 |archive-date=2015-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008064023/http://collider.com/the-equalizer-2-release-date/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年9月，宣布電影於2017年9月開拍，法奎和華盛頓都確認回歸。

